stories.title: Portsmouth council votes to address 'housing crisis' with action plan
Cinde Warmington launches second bid for New Hampshire governor
Seacoast home prices smash records as the median price tops $1 million
stories.summary: Median sales price of Seacoast single-family homes exceeded $1 million in January 2026 for the first time — $1,087,500, up 25.5% from January 2025. Presents the data as a market record, not as a displacement or affordability crisis indicator.
